                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic">policeman.</hi>) I apprehended the prisoner—he said he went into the shop for half an ounce of tobacco and laid down 1 1/2 <hi rend="italic">d</hi>. on the counter—he came out without the tobacco or the halfpence.</p>
